{
  "scene_id": "grey_march",
  "entries": [
    {
      "id": "grey_march_001",
      "speaker": "torren",
      "lines": [
        "The spirits stop here. They won't go further."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "grey_march_002",
      "speaker": "sable",
      "lines": [
        "Smart spirits."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "grey_march_003",
      "speaker": "maren",
      "lines": [
        "The Convergence draws the Pallor to it like a drain.\nEverything alive pulls away. What's left is... this."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "grey_march_004",
      "speaker": "edren",
      "lines": [
        "How far?"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "grey_march_005",
      "speaker": "maren",
      "lines": [
        "Two days through the Wastes. There are trial clearings\nalong the route — places where the Pallor concentrates. Ancient.\nOlder than the Archive."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "grey_march_006",
      "speaker": "lira",
      "lines": [
        "Trial clearings?"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "grey_march_007",
      "speaker": "maren",
      "lines": [
        "The Archivist mentioned them. In previous cycles,\nanyone approaching the Convergence had to pass through them. The\nPallor tests you. It finds the thing you're most afraid of and\nmakes you face it."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "grey_march_008",
      "speaker": "sable",
      "lines": [
        "Wonderful. Any other cheerful news?"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "grey_march_009",
      "speaker": "maren",
      "lines": [
        "Yes. You can't avoid them. The path goes through."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "grey_march_010",
      "speaker": "torren",
      "lines": [
        "It's still alive in there. Somewhere. Just... not\nenough to move."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "grey_march_011",
      "speaker": "sable",
      "lines": [
        "Listen. No birds."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "grey_march_012",
      "speaker": "edren",
      "lines": [
        "Since when?"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "grey_march_013",
      "speaker": "sable",
      "lines": [
        "Since the last ridge. Nothing singing. Nothing flying.\nNothing."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "grey_march_014",
      "speaker": "maren",
      "lines": [
        "Past here, the trials begin. The Pallor will test\neach of us. It finds what you fear most and makes you face it."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": [
        {
          "line": 0,
          "id": "pallor_ambience"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "grey_march_015",
      "speaker": "sable",
      "lines": [
        "And? What if you can't face it?"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "grey_march_016",
      "speaker": "maren",
      "lines": [
        "Then you stay. Like the deer. Like the bird."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    }
  ]
}
